Sentencas: La0.65Ca0.35FeO3-delta-Gd0.2Ce0.8O2-delta (LCF-GDC) material is synthesized and studied as a new Sr and Co-free composite cathode for solid-oxide fuel cells (SOFC) at intermediate temperatures.
Titulo: Developing a new Sr and Co-free composite cathode of solid oxide fuel cells with high performance

Sentencas: The XRD analysis reveals that the LCF powder exhibits excellent phase stability and compatibility with the GDC electrolytes.
Titulo: Developing a new Sr and Co-free composite cathode of solid oxide fuel cells with high performance

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity of LCF is exceeding 100 S.cm(-1) at a temperature above 650 ? and reaches a maximum value of 112 S. cm(-1) at 800 ?.
Titulo: Developing a new Sr and Co-free composite cathode of solid oxide fuel cells with high performance

Sentencas: The peak power density of the single-cell with LCF-GDC composite cathode achieves 1.172 W. cm(-2) with a low R-p value of 0.28 omega cm(2) at 750 ?.
Titulo: Developing a new Sr and Co-free composite cathode of solid oxide fuel cells with high performance
